a to start up a criminal organization guild before Mr. Brust came around and stole my ingenius ideas of Interplanetary Server Economic Domination <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  (I love typing that!). <p>Vall Shadowstrife <BR>
